<section class="bay-area" id="about">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">For Bay Area Minds</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center text-muted">
      Let us translate this property into familiar terms.
    </p>

    <div class="translation-grid">
      <div class="translation-card">
        <span class="translation-label">Land</span>
        <span class="translation-value">~70,000 sqm</span>
        <span class="translation-context">17.3 acres, about 13 American football fields</span>
      </div>

      <div class="translation-card">
        <span class="translation-label">Built Area</span>
        <span class="translation-value">3,000+ sqm</span>
        <span class="translation-context">32,000+ sq ft across 13 structures</span>
      </div>

      <div class="translation-card">
        <span class="translation-label">Price</span>
        <span class="translation-value">€1,890,000</span>
        <span class="translation-context">Less than a 2BR in the Mission</span>
      </div>

      <div class="translation-card">
        <span class="translation-label">What You Get</span>
        <span class="translation-value">A village</span>
        <span class="translation-context">Jungle canopy, ocean views, buildable land</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="translation-narrative">
      <p>
        In the Bay Area, €1.89M buys you a modest single-family home, maybe with a view
        if you are lucky. Here, that same capital acquires a compound: thirteen independent
        buildings on a jungle hillside, above the surf, minutes from an international airport.
      </p>
      <p>
        This is not a compromise. It is an arbitrage on quality of life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bay-area {
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .translation-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .translation-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .translation-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .translation-value {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .translation-context {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .translation-narrative {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .translation-narrative p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .translation-narrative p:last-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
